    <title>Attach your network to an existing server</title>
    <para>You can attach your network to existing servers by using the Nova-Network API. The Neutron API does not provide an
        equivalent operation. See the
        <link xlink:href="http://docs.rackspace.com/servers/api/v2/cs-gettingstarted/content/ch_gs_getting_started_with_nova.html">
                Cloud Servers Getting Started Guide</link>
        for examples of attaching a network to an existing server by using the Nova-Network API and the &virt_ext;</para>
